# Provider auto-upgrade

When the user asks to implement all platforms, continue upgrades, or process the queue:

1. Read skill `.cursor/skills/mediacore-upgrade-loop/SKILL.md`.
2. Run `uv run python scripts/provider_upgrade_queue.py next --limit 5`.
3. Upgrade that batch only (oEmbed / official API → working provider; else hosts_only or skipped_no_api).
4. Mark queue statuses; refresh docs + `DOCS_WORKING_STATUS`; run provider tests.

## yt-dlp

Use https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/tree/master/yt_dlp/extractor only to learn **hosts / `_VALID_URL` / IE names**.

Never port scrape or download logic from yt-dlp into MediaCore.
